msgstr "Publicat Xfce 4.20"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "After almost two years of work, we are happy to announce the release of Xfce 4.20 !\n"
msgstr "Després de gairebé dos anys de treball, estem contents d'anunciar el llançament de l'Xfce 4.20!\n"

#. type: Plain text
